text: Paragnorima is a genus of moths belonging to the subfamily Thyatirinae of the Drepanidae. ==Species== * Paragnorima fuscescens (Hampson, 1893) ==Former species== * Paragnorima brunnea Leech, 1900 * Paragnorima transitans (Houlbert, 1921) ==References== * , 1912, in Seitz, Die Gross-Schmetterlinge der Erde 2: 329 * , 2007, Esperiana Buchreihe zur Entomologie Band 13: 1-683 Category:Thyatirinae Category:Drepanidae genera
title: Paragnorima
